we can do this: 

```
func (c *CycleState) SetRecordFrameworkMetrics() {
	if c == nil {
		return
	}
        const sampleRate = 10  // 10% sample rate
        c.recordFrameworkMetrics = false
        if rand.Intn(100) < sampleRate {
          c.recordFrameworkMetrics = true
      }
}
```

```rand.Intn``` is in  ```"math/rand"```

